<p>I want to make a set of radio buttons sticky in rails. I can do that with a text field with:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;%= text_field_tag :name, @help_name %&gt; </code></pre>  <p>where <code>@help_name</code> makes the tag sticky. </p>  <p>I have the following radio buttons. </p>  <pre><code>&lt;%= radio_button_tag 'urgency', "low", false %&gt; Low: &lt;br/&gt; &lt;%= radio_button_tag 'urgency', "medium", false %&gt; Medium: &lt;br/&gt; &lt;%= radio_button_tag 'urgency', "high", false %&gt;  High: &lt;br/&gt; &lt;%= radio_button_tag 'urgency', "low", false %&gt; Work Stoppage&lt;br/&gt; </code></pre>  <p>How do I make those sticky as well?</p>